    "[…] Cysts: Bone cysts, such as subchondral cysts, can also create opacities.",
    "(Bone) cysts do not cause 'opacities' but 'lucencies'.",
    "[Radiography] What could explain the finding (i.e., Segond fracture) in the tibial plateau?",
    "[…] Bone erosion: In certain conditions like rheumatoid arthritis, there can be bone erosions, which can present as opacities on thex-ray image.Erosions do not cause 'opacities' but 'lucencies'.",
